overview: The user initiated a comprehensive review of their sleep questionnaire
  application to verify adherence to the Statement of Work and detailed
  questionnaire specifications. The assistant conducted a thorough analysis of
  the codebase, identifying both well-implemented features like the interactive
  questionnaire, database storage, CSV export, PDF report generation, and admin
  dashboard, as well as several critical gaps. High-priority missing items
  included a 1-10 tiredness severity scale with safety warnings, COMISA
  detection, outbound links in reports, and weighted scoring for Excessive
  Daytime Sleepiness. The assistant then began implementing the first
  high-priority task, successfully integrating the tiredness severity scale into
  the application's data types, validation, and user interface, including a
  safety alert for severe tiredness levels.
